xyz.swatt.selenium

Class WebElementTransitionalWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.swatt.selenium.WebElementWrapper
      • xyz.swatt.selenium.WebElementTransitionalWrapper

  • public class WebElementTransitionalWrapper
extends WebElementWrapper
    This Class extends WebElementWrapper and contains all of it's functionality.

    The only difference is that this class has the getWebElement() method.

    The purpose of this class is to be used temporarily, while transitioning an existing project to SWATT.

    Author:
    Brandon Dudek (BrandonDudek)
